data.description: Open House Saturday December 8th 11am-12pm! For sale, not for rent.  Beautifully redone from the studs out in 2022!  Lovely light interior with laminate flooring, granite countertops (breakfast bar in the kitchen) and large vanity in the bathroom with an XL tile shower. Comes with washer, dryer, and refrigerator plus pots seen in photo!  Large laundry closet with storage.  Huge backyard and slab for outdoor living or parking. Fence with rolling gate is  2022.  Roof, H20 heater, plumbing, electrical, appliances, windows, doors, and HVAC 2022!  Location is super convenient to stores, schools, dining & SPID. Adorable home and backyard with recent rock landscaping and storage shed is MOVE IN READY. On a .23 acre lot, you'll enjoy a huge private outdoor living space to create your vision.
